{
  "stem": "19969.7",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Czechoslovakia was forced it, but Hungary and Romania and-- and Bulgaria were all full partners with Hitler.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he said that Hitler issued an order to the king of Bulgaria [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that 25,000 Jews-- they always set a quota, I found out, in Italy and wherever-- that they were to send into to Germany for extermination.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the Bulgarian king refused to do it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we have a parliament Bulgaria and the parliament refused.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So the king was ordered to go to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He went, came back, and died very mysteriously several days later.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The Bulgarians say he was poisoned somehow or other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But then Hitler made a-- he lowered the demand from 25,000 to 20,000 and the Bulgarians still refused.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he didn't-- Hitler didn't do anything about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So Bulgaria was apparently the only country that refused to-- to round up any Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I found out in Italy, they got a quota the same way, but Italians, while they sent quite a few Jews, they didn't round them up the way Hitler ordered them to.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They would always make an excuse they didn't have a transport for-- they use the word transport over there for the trains, you know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the Italians dragged their feet a lot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And so not many Jews were taken out of Italy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Mussolini wasn't much in favor of taking the Jews out for extermination.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I didn't know anything about concentration camps before the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Only after the war on various travels that I've made to countries of Europe and meeting with people who were in those countries or prisoners or like this Bulgarian professor who migrated to the United States, was now a professor in-- at Emory University in Atlanta.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
